{"tid":2164444,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你班感情台MK 女體自主撚收爺啦","createTime":"2020-08-19T08:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T09:55:17.000Z","uid":886,"like":25,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d42d35263fd5b2fe111096c36fb9f3c2520c876f","tid":2164444,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:00:48.000Z","msg":"段片係邊個放都好啦<br />\n而家個個見倒條仔都話好撚正又長又有錢<br />\n條女就臭雞SLUT，玩到咁放盪唔知點見人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現實就係咁<br />\n跟本唔係真係要你塊膜，係要你純潔無邪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男人食得多女=勁，女人比人屌得多就係雞係公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大把女去晒酒店吹晒波波慶祝生日post上網<br />\n係人都知影完相咪爆房囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩撚完散左hide左D相，咪下一個囉<br />\n喂，第時點同個女交代啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你老母我當年就係咁年少輕狂有咁既過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你千其唔好學你老母我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係連登話唔介意果D仔<br />\n將心比己<br />\n兩個一樣，一個處一個唔係處<br />\n有得你揀真係會要個非處咩 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nD女人唔係處係肉體上情感上已經係次貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女體自主跟本就係一個騙局黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除非你好似email咁用身體黎搵錢 <span class=\"small\">(我會好Respect你)</span><br />\n<br />\n希望各位仲純潔既女女唔好比人氹兩氹就比左個處人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪聽班感情台MK講到咁大愛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲可以大大聲當面屌柒D臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係處女啊，你係唔係啊 ? 吓，你地比人呃左啊? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申定先：<br />\n食過20條女UP，咪攻擊我話我冇溝過女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現實大把女人出軌派帽偷食追撚含多的是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab98b247d483f8a0dd8158c3d7da9f3ea9b1d8d5","tid":2164444,"uid":197005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:01:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06e22ee9d921cb1c60a9e5e5fd716952f8c0242c","tid":2164444,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ab98b247d483f8a0dd8158c3d7da9f3ea9b1d8d5","tid":2164444,"uid":197005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:01:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=